dct_description_sm: Map of the Chinese province Shan-tung showing province and colonial boundaries, transportation, communications, ground and water features, missions and populated places. Relief shown by shading, hachures and spot heights. Includes an English, Chinese explanation and a list of sources of information. "T.S.G.S. No. 1936."
dct_creator_sm: Great Britain. War Office. General Staff. Topographical Section
dct_publisher_sm: Southampton : Reproduced and printed for the Topographical Section, General Staff, at the Ordnance Survey Office, 1905.
